    <article>
        <p>I can&#39;t stand out of office auto-replies. </p>
<p>I send a message to 10 people and 3 back. I don&#39;t care that you took off on friday. </p>
<p>It would be great if when you send out an email you can tack on #noOOO or something like that, and the auto-reply system will not send those back. </p>
<p>Or maybe reverse it and say  #yesOOO  and OOO messages will only be sent when people really want them (which in most cases will be never).</p>

